Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈让你来和爸爸道别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后一次能够触碰到故人机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好好和他道别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,冷冰冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,帮爸爸擦一擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,突然从头上浇水的话 爸爸会说「好冷」的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有你的信 我放你桌上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(54,248)\fad(300,300)}Last Episode \N\N\N\N最后的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs13\pos(55,226)\fad(300,300)}eternal engage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,到底要怎么办啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在吗？ 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我有毛病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟游同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,最近没联络过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你们俩吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,倒不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你们肯定吵架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真讨厌啊 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是凸守啊 凸守早苗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,恶心？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你吃了暗黑树根了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼才会吃那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你啊 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你那头发是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没啦 就觉得双马尾有点幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫我学长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,学长 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,快闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你用这种说话风格超不自然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,放手啦 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,头发可是女性的生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能这么粗鲁的乱拽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你这也太突然了吧 搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只是 从那之后我想了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 不 小鸟游学姐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs13\pos(225,328)}master
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还有学长你说的那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太 学姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,久民学姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这美少女是怎么回事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,五月七日同学 你眼睛怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,只是感冒的话还好办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 只要喝下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,久民学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 那副打扮是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好丢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你有资格说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛是也啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是也？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,难道这家伙是初中生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你才发觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs13}Dark Flame Master\N{\fs20}暗黑火焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,请别这么叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要看看我的眼睛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？ 别这么冷淡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 说起来 为什么你要模仿六花？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 这不是模仿 而是传承
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是得到了邪王真眼的传承
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,传承？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 在上一个朔月之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她把全部黑暗之力都托付给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 我是邪王真眼的继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别啊 那种东西不用继承也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:06:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,邪王真眼必须永存于世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只要暗黑火焰使还在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs13\pos(320,328)}Dark Flame Master
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是六花这么说的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好帅的样子 是也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,结果你到底想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一口气收拾完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧 不过仔细想想我们也没搞过什么活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 话剧部那边怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,去是去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说 部长是个过于热血的学长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么 我们来制作只有我们能够创造的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是新时代蕴含的无限的可能性啊 什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 确实有这种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是说热血就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好是好 就是听起来给人一种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:07:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,「呃 这货是中二病啊」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那能算中二病吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,或许和中二病不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有种 自己和别人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只有自己察觉到了 所以自己是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,非常容易陷进这种妄想里的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 你和我都从中二病毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,心想 高中一定要像普通人一样度过不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这也不过是自己擅自捏造了一个普通高中生的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后被其束缚着而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只是觉得人们说到底都总是痴迷于什么东西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好深奥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为你太肤浅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 我来洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你看着又会把餐具摔碎的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？ 我摔碎过那么多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道小鸟游不在了你感到很寂寞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她也不是不在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我也没什么好寂寞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,傍晚搬家公司的人来过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过会回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你说只是去去就来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在出发不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,到半路就没电车了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈和爷爷奶奶看起来都很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应的话他们会很放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我想这样一定是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太你也这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？ 结果都是我说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,叫她摘下眼罩是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,叫她从中二病毕业的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,全是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}与勇气同在的好友 勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Dark Flame Master 敬上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Flame…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,当你读到这封信时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你说不定已经不再是暗黑火焰使了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs13\pos(403,329)}Dark Flame Master
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是因为2012年 根据玛雅文明的预言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,毁灭世界的浪潮将吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你的精神波动被弱化了的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你将看透一切 放弃努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只是享受眼前的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,变成了愚蠢的普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在已然感觉到了预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以写了这封信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,暗黑火焰使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs13\pos(310,328)}Dark Flame Master
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,别被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是拥有力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是被暗黑之王 邪王所选召的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别无他选 是特别的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,初二时写给两年后的自己的信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是些什么啊 好傻啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在家附近的游戏中心拿的游戏币啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么力量都没有啦 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,反面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,借你是可以啦 这么晚了你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,去接六花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟游…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你难不成？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 我想对她说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想为她做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs13}Dark Flame Master\N{\fs20}暗黑火焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,本人邪王真眼二代 有话要传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 爸爸去世了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那时完全没有实感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的心来不及感受现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我想爸爸的病一定能马上治好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,直到爸爸去世的那天早上 还是那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那时遇到了勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到我？ 六花她？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 六花…不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,邪王真眼在两年前邂逅了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就在去圣调理人的住处时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs13\pos(308,328)}Priestess
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:12:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,搬家？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 不过你想在爷爷家住也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们的房子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是啊 没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 别闹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,空气太黏腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这表示 它在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,从那之后 她每天都在注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？ 在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那里也有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,终于能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁！ 我被谁监视着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,六花当时就觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你的那些想法真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,比起压抑真实的想法 只能默默顺从的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你显得更加坦诚 更加出色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那 这算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她 还有她的中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,六花是被中二病拯救了的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,并憧憬着中二病和这种妄想力量的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想让你看到自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想模仿你的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才会选择你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,非你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,六花她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一直…一直一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,六花！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,得浇水了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟游六花…不…邪王真眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,缔结契约吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谁！ 小偷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 你想干嘛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老婆子 快叫警察来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,六花 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你要回到无聊的现实里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还是 和我一起改变现实？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老婆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 色狼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 制造点状况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来让大爷摸一摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,站住 不许动！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啊 我是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他们会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,快 动作迅速是也！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托小凸家的人开车送我们来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你小子 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,脚好像抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我来骑吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 只要有暗黑火焰使的力量在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs13\pos(344,329)}Dark Flame Master
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这点程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,光…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是船的灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只是人造光而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,下车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是黑暗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,引爆吧现实！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,迸射吧精神！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs13}Punishment this world\N{\fs20}神罚卍于卍世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是不可视境界线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那些光点在注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,传达吧 把你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把你一直说不出口的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,永别了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都说 中二病是丢人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不想再想起那段时光了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,想从脑子里删除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 那时的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,行为怪异的自己真的会从此消失吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妄想着自己被谁监视着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,设定自己的形象 并装扮一番
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,人有时会口出狂言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想象不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,展望遥远的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,描绘着并不存在的轰轰烈烈的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那是从出生到步入坟墓为止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在生活中周而复始地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,无尽地重复着的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,悲伤的 害羞的 并令人怜爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,名为自我意识过剩的——痼疾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,名为自我的 不可逃避的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我们永远患着中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要看看 我的眼睛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:21:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,中二病好丢人！
